==職業生涯==
===波士頓紅襪===
2010年6月28日，杜布朗特升上大聯盟。他以先發5局失3分拿下大聯盟首勝。<ref>{{cite news|title=Ortiz homers as Red Sox beat Dodgers in Manny return|url=http://scores.espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=300618102|accessdate=July 31, 2014|agency=Associated Press|work=ESPN.com|date=June 18, 2010|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304112654/http://scores.espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=300618102|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2012年，他成功擠進紅襪先發名單內。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Abraham|first1=Peter|title=Doubront, Bard put in rotation|url=http://www.boston.com/sports/baseball/redsox/articles/2012/04/02/red_sox_pick_doubront_and_bard_for_rotation/|accessdate=July 31, 2014|publisher=Boston Globe|date=April 2, 2012|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304214425/http://www.boston.com/sports/baseball/redsox/articles/2012/04/02/red_sox_pick_doubront_and_bard_for_rotation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在前10場先發拿下5勝2敗，最後他拿下11勝10敗。<ref name="BR">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/d/doubrfe01.shtml|title=Felix Doubront Statistics & History|work=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=April 2, 2015|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502232727/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/d/doubrfe01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年，杜布朗特投出他在大聯盟生涯表現最好的一季。該年他拿下11勝6敗，<ref name="BR"/>球隊也拿下97勝闖進季後賽。當時他在季後賽多擔任牛棚投手，最終紅襪順利拿下世界大賽冠軍。

2014年球季初，杜布朗特陷入低潮。他在5月份因為某次肩膀撞到車門受傷，導致他表現不穩定被拔除先發位置。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hardballtalk.nbcsports.com/2014/05/21/felix-doubront-hurt-his-shoulder-on-a-car-door/|title=Felix Doubront hurt his shoulder on a car door|last=Gleeman|first=Aaron|work=hardballtalk.nbcsports.com|date=May 21, 2014|accessdate=April 2, 2015|archive-date=2014-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140723023804/http://hardballtalk.nbcsports.com/2014/05/21/felix-doubront-hurt-his-shoulder-on-a-car-door/|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月28日，他面對藍鳥僅投了0.2局就狂失6分。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nesn.com/2014/07/felix-doubront-john-farrell-had-meeting-after-implosion-vs-blue-jays/|title=Felix Doubront, John Farrell Had Meeting After Implosion Vs. Blue Jays|last=Doyle|first=Ricky|work=nesn.com|date=July 29, 2014|accessdate=April 2, 2015|archive-date=2018-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180910061027/https://nesn.com/2014/07/felix-doubront-john-farrell-had-meeting-after-implosion-vs-blue-jays/|dead-url=no}}</ref>過了兩天他就被球隊交易，最後留下2勝4敗，防禦率6.07的數據。

===芝加哥小熊===
2014年7月30日，紅襪隊將他交易至小熊，換來一名日後指定球員(Marco Hernández)。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/eye-on-baseball/24643438/red-sox-trade-felix-doubront-to-cubs|title=Red Sox trade Felix Doubront to Cubs|last=Perry|first=Dayn|work=cbssports.com|date=July 30, 2014|accessdate=July 30, 2014|archive-date=2016-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160522143739/http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/eye-on-baseball/24643438/red-sox-trade-felix-doubront-to-cubs|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Cohen|first1=Jay|last2=Golen|first2=Jimmy|title=Cubs acquire struggling LHP Doubront from Red Sox|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/wire?section=mlb&id=11289830|accessdate=July 31, 2014|agency=Associated Press|work=ESPN.com|date=July 31, 2014|archive-date=2015-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150705073701/http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/wire?section=mlb&id=11289830|dead-url=no}}</ref>他才一到小熊隊就直接進傷兵。最終他僅出賽4場比賽，拿下2勝1敗，防禦率3.98。2015年3月28日，小熊隊將他釋出。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2015/03/cubs-release-felix-doubront.html|title=Cubs Release Felix Doubront|last=Wilmoth|first=Charlie|work=mlbtraderumors.com|date=March 28, 2015|accessdate=April 2, 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108110414/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2015/03/cubs-release-felix-doubront.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===多倫多藍鳥===
2015年4月2日，杜布朗特與藍鳥隊簽下小聯盟合約。<ref name="Blue Jays">{{cite web|url=http://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/person-interest-411-felix-doubront/|title=Person of Interest: The 411 on Felix Doubront|last=Simmons|first=Jeff|work=[[Sportsnet|Sportsnet]]|date=April 2, 2015|accessdate=April 2, 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108152230/https://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/person-interest-411-felix-doubront/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在7月初升上大聯盟，後援了2.1局。7月7日，他在藍鳥隊的初次先發就拿下勝投。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/doubront-buys-time-for-blue-jays-to-figure-out-rotation/|title=Doubront buys time for Blue Jays to figure out rotation|last=Davidi|first=Shi|work=[[Sportsnet|Sportsnet]]|date=July 7, 2015|accessdate=July 8, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309151226/http://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/doubront-buys-time-for-blue-jays-to-figure-out-rotation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過最後他在7月29日遭到球隊指定讓渡，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/blue-jays-designate-felix-doubront-for-assignment/|title=Blue Jays designate Felix Doubront for assignment|last=Nicholson-Smith|first=Ben|work=[[Sportsnet|Sportsnet]]|date=July 29, 2015|accessdate=July 29, 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108092003/https://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/blue-jays-designate-felix-doubront-for-assignment/|dead-url=no}}</ref>最終留下1勝1敗，防禦率4.76的成績。

===奧克蘭運動家===
2015年7月31日，他被交易至運動家。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.athletics.mlb.com/news/article/140128112|title=A's acquire Doubront from Blue Jays for cash|work=MLB.com|date=July 31, 2015|accessdate=July 31, 2015|first=Cash|last=Kruth|archive-date=2016-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160425222558/http://m.athletics.mlb.com/news/article/140128112|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/Athletics/status/627199691571105792?lang=en|title=Oakland Athletics 🌳🐘⚾️ on Twitter|publisher=|access-date=2020-12-30|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305144529/https://twitter.com/Athletics/status/627199691571105792?lang=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年他在運動家投出2勝2敗，防禦率5.81。隔年他因為動了湯米·約翰手術導致整季報銷。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Koo|first1=Jeremy|title=Doubront to have Tommy John surgery.|url=http://www.athleticsnation.com/2016/4/11/11410422/oakland-as-announce-felix-doubront-will-have-tommy-john-surgery|website=athleticsnation.com|publisher=Athletics Nation|accessdate=April 11, 2016|archive-date=2018-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181128034910/https://www.athleticsnation.com/2016/4/11/11410422/oakland-as-announce-felix-doubront-will-have-tommy-john-surgery|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年10月7日，他成為自由球員。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.scout.com/mlb/athletics/story/1714883-a-s-outright-three-more-to-triple-a |title=Oakland A's outright three more to Triple-A |first=Melissa |last=Lockard |date=October 7, 2016 |accessdate=October 7, 2016 |archive-date=2017-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170718035419/http://www.scout.com/mlb/athletics/story/1714883-a-s-outright-three-more-to-triple-a |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.athleticsnation.com/2016/10/7/13207854/oakland-as-roster-moves-eric-sogard-jarrod-parker-free-agency |title=Oakland A's roster moves: Eric Sogard, Jarrod Parker, 4 others head to free agency |first=Alex |last=Hall |date=October 7, 2016 |accessdate=October 7, 2016 |archive-date=2018-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180624093114/https://www.athleticsnation.com/2016/10/7/13207854/oakland-as-roster-moves-eric-sogard-jarrod-parker-free-agency |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過後來他又與球隊續約，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sfgate.com/athletics/article/A-s-re-sign-Felix-Doubront-Matt-McBride-10616905.php |title=A's re-sign Felix Doubront, Matt McBride |first=Susan |last=Slusser |date=November 15, 2016 |accessdate=November 16, 2016 |work=sfgate.com |archive-date=2017-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171108152048/http://www.sfgate.com/athletics/article/A-s-re-sign-Felix-Doubront-Matt-McBride-10616905.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/minor-league-transactions-nov-12-18/#Cdo3LoKr4XPZbC2h.97|title=Minor League Transactions: Nov 12-18|last=Eddy|first=Matt|work=baseballamerica.com|date=November 21, 2016|accessdate=November 21, 2016|archive-date=2017-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812040125/http://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/minor-league-transactions-nov-12-18/#Cdo3LoKr4XPZbC2h.97|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在2017年球季結束後又成為自由球員。

===樂天巨人===
2017年12月14日，杜布朗特以一年100萬美元的合約加盟韓職的樂天巨人。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/news/2017/12/14/0200000000AEN20171214005500315.html|title=Lotte Giants agree to terms with ex-MLB pitcher Felix Doubront|work=english.yonhapnews.co.kr|date=December 14, 2017|accessdate=December 19, 2017|archive-date=2017-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222053012/http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/news/2017/12/14/0200000000AEN20171214005500315.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而他僅先發3場全敗，防禦率高達13.50。最終他在9月份遭到球隊揮棄。<ref>[https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2018/09/lotte-giants-place-felix-doubront-on-waivers.html Lotte Giants place Felix Doubront on waivers] {{Wayback|url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2018/09/lotte-giants-place-felix-doubront-on-waivers.html |date=20210125235226 }}. ''Baseball Reference''. Retrieved on September 12, 2018.</ref>

===普埃布拉鸚鵡===
2019年2月14日，杜布朗特與墨西哥聯盟的普埃布拉鸚鵡簽下合約。不過他在5月3日遭到釋出。

===薩爾蒂約瑟拉佩穿衣者===
2019年5月14日，杜布朗特加盟墨西哥聯盟的瑟拉佩穿衣者隊。

===統一7-ELEVEn獅===
2021年1月5日，杜布朗特加盟中職的統一7-ELEVEn獅。中文登錄名為「飛力士」。

